into a filthy nursing home

300
00:14:05,928 --> 00:14:08,038
so fast you won't know what hit you.

301
00:14:08,305 --> 00:14:10,541
Probably, it'll be a filthy nurse.

302
00:14:10,666 --> 00:14:14,344
Leela, you're my daughter
and I love you, but cram it!

303
00:14:14,469 --> 00:14:15,813
Morris:
Is this a bad time?

304
00:14:15,979 --> 00:14:17,548
I was riding the el torito
dinner backwash,

305
00:14:17,673 --> 00:14:18,858
and I thought I'd pop in.

306
00:14:19,024 --> 00:14:20,050
Oh, thank God you're here.

307
00:14:20,175 --> 00:14:21,485
If we don't do something,

308
00:14:21,610 --> 00:14:23,738
mom's going to marry Zapp Brannigan!

309
00:14:23,904 --> 00:14:25,956
So? He seems like a nice kahuna.

310
00:14:26,081 --> 00:14:28,325
Dad, stop being so mellow.

311
00:14:28,450 --> 00:14:30,620
Leela, honey, chill out.

312
00:14:30,786 --> 00:14:32,529
You got to take the good
with the gnarly.

313
00:14:32,654 --> 00:14:35,298
Speaking of which, time for me
to shoot the ihop dessert curl.

314
00:14:35,423 --> 00:14:36,793
(Wave splashes)

315
00:14:36,959 --> 00:14:38,711
(Groans)

316
00:14:44,967 --> 00:14:47,544
Oh, you sure you won't come
to your mom's wedding?

317
00:14:47,669 --> 00:14:49,806
There'll be
"chicken or fish, circle one."

318
00:14:49,972 --> 00:14:51,147
I can't.

319
00:14:51,272 --> 00:14:52,382
Not when I believe with all my heart

320
00:14:52,507 --> 00:14:54,060
that this marriage is a mistake.

321
00:14:54,226 --> 00:14:56,720
I know you're upset
that your parents broke up.

322
00:14:56,845 --> 00:14:59,816
But what if Zapp really
does make Munda happy?

323
00:14:59,982 --> 00:15:02,109
What if they're meant to be together?

324
00:15:02,275 --> 00:15:03,426
Fry, that's just so...

325
00:15:03,551 --> 00:15:04,995
I can't even believe...

326
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,530
You are so totally...

327
00:15:06,655 --> 00:15:07,931
Right.

328
00:15:08,056 --> 00:15:09,450
You're right.

329
00:15:09,616 --> 00:15:11,167
I am? Huh.

330
00:15:11,292 --> 00:15:14,247
Maybe Zapp isn't the only one
who's marriage material.

331
00:15:15,530 --> 00:15:17,166
You're getting there.

332
00:15:23,238 --> 00:15:25,591
(Grunting)

333
00:15:31,379 --> 00:15:32,523
Leela?

334
00:15:32,648 --> 00:15:33,790
You look beautiful, mom.

335
00:15:33,915 --> 00:15:35,358
Really?

336
00:15:35,483 --> 00:15:38,688
I'm not showing too much
sucker for a lady my age?

337
00:15:38,854 --> 00:15:39,963
Just the right amount.

338
00:15:40,088 --> 00:15:41,464
You'll make a lovely bride.

339
00:15:41,589 --> 00:15:43,109
Oh, mom...

340
00:15:43,275 --> 00:15:46,112
I'm sorry I've been
so horrible to you.

341
00:15:46,278 --> 00:15:48,271
Ah, you weren't so horrible.

342
00:15:48,396 --> 00:15:50,765
Just enough to show you care.

343
00:15:53,243 --> 00:15:55,580
♪

344
00:16:06,715 --> 00:16:07,958
At ease, darling.

345
00:16:08,083 --> 00:16:10,594
Honored guests...
And Kif.

346
00:16:10,719 --> 00:16:12,796
One of a captain's many superpowers

347
00:16:12,921 --> 00:16:15,599
is the ability to conduct marriage.

348
00:16:15,724 --> 00:16:19,169
So I will now join myself
in holy macaroni.

349
00:16:19,294 --> 00:16:22,505
Kif, raise the ceremonial mirror.

350
00:16:22,773 --> 00:16:24,908
Zapp, you magnificent bastard,

351
00:16:25,033 --> 00:16:26,735
do you take Munda
to be your lawful...

352
00:16:26,860 --> 00:16:27,820
(Alarms whoop)

353
00:16:28,779 --> 00:16:30,948
Alien ships approaching, sir.

354
00:16:34,618 --> 00:16:37,020
It's the Carcarons!
Oh, meatballs.

355
00:16:37,145 --> 00:16:39,749
I forgot they were coming
to sign the peace treaty today.

356
00:16:39,915 --> 00:16:42,859
Ladies and gentlemen,
my blushing translator and I

357
00:16:42,984 --> 00:16:44,294
