377
00:17:33,334 --> 00:17:35,178
Now, let's tell these vicious lies

378
00:17:35,303 --> 00:17:36,680
and get back to our sacred vows.

379
00:17:36,805 --> 00:17:38,515
There's not going to be any wedding.

380
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:40,250
I don't want your fancy ring.

381
00:17:40,517 --> 00:17:42,418
Careful! That's glass!

382
00:17:42,686 --> 00:17:43,887
Leela was right.

383
00:17:44,012 --> 00:17:45,889
You're a lousy man
and a lousy captain.

384
00:17:46,014 --> 00:17:49,026
And I'm going to tell our
Carcaron friends the truth.

385
00:17:49,192 --> 00:17:50,827
(Speaking alien language)

386
00:17:50,952 --> 00:17:53,220
Zapp... lying sack of...

387
