392
00:18:10,071 --> 00:18:11,948
We're under attack
and the wedding's off.

393
00:18:12,073 --> 00:18:14,343
Kif, return fire and the cake.

394
00:18:14,509 --> 00:18:16,286
Our weapons are disabled,

395
00:18:16,411 --> 00:18:17,954
and you can't return ice cream cakes!

396
00:18:18,079 --> 00:18:19,306
We're doomed!

397
00:18:19,472 --> 00:18:21,682
(Clattering)

398
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:24,145
Stop the wedding!

399
00:18:24,311 --> 00:18:25,980
(Gasping, exclaiming)
Morris?

400
00:18:26,146 --> 00:18:28,264
I'm not giving up the love
of my life without a fight.

401
00:18:28,389 --> 00:18:29,532
(Grunts)

402
00:18:29,657 --> 00:18:31,986
Do I know you?
(Groans)

403
00:18:32,152 --> 00:18:33,136
Dad?

404
00:18:33,261 --> 00:18:34,404
I thought you were all zen

405
00:18:34,529 --> 00:18:35,865
with mom getting remarried.

406
00:18:36,031 --> 00:18:37,107
I was at first.

407
00:18:37,232 --> 00:18:38,942
But then I conquered my inner peace.

408
00:18:39,067 --> 00:18:42,245
If you care about something,
you've got to take action.

409
00:18:42,370 --> 00:18:44,748
Harsh, violent action!

410
00:18:44,873 --> 00:18:46,292
(Screaming)

411
00:18:50,378 --> 00:18:51,672
Kif, get us out of here.

412
00:18:51,838 --> 00:18:53,990
Navigation is out.

413
00:18:54,115 --> 00:18:55,718
We're sitting ducks.

414
00:18:55,884 --> 00:18:57,636
