separate control keys.

417
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:02,766
No one could work them well enough

418
00:19:02,891 --> 00:19:04,167
to ride out these energy waves.

419
00:19:04,292 --> 00:19:05,559
No one?

420
00:19:08,271 --> 00:19:10,173
It's time to hang 20!

421
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:12,843
Munda:
Morris!

422
00:19:13,109 --> 00:19:15,411
What are you doing?
Hold on to your coconuts.

423
00:19:15,695 --> 00:19:18,115
We're going for
the ride of a lifetime!

424
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:21,035
♪

425
00:19:24,246 --> 00:19:26,916
but I thought you were
terrified of outer space.

426
00:19:27,082 --> 00:19:28,524
I was, but then it hit me.

427
00:19:28,649 --> 00:19:30,360
If heaven's above us,

428
00:19:30,485 --> 00:19:34,821
then the whole universe
is just God's glorious sewer.

429
00:19:44,224 --> 00:19:45,851
(Grunting)

430
00:19:46,017 --> 00:19:47,443
Hang on, sweetie!

431
00:19:47,727 --> 00:19:48,678
(Alarm blaring)

432
00:19:48,803 --> 00:19:50,814
What do we do?
Who do we blame?

433
00:19:50,939 --> 00:19:52,115
We don't blame anyone.

434
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:53,526
We make peace.

435
00:19:53,692 --> 00:19:55,361
One word can end this.

436
00:19:55,527 --> 00:19:56,362
