437
00:19:56,528 --> 00:19:59,323
No, you say it.

438
00:20:00,348 --> 00:20:02,058
(Clears throat)

439
00:20:02,183 --> 00:20:04,051
(Speaks alien language)

440
00:20:09,190 --> 00:20:10,709
(Grunts in agreement)

441
00:20:17,465 --> 00:20:21,244
This actual peace treaty
is hereby enacted.

442
00:20:21,511 --> 00:20:23,764
